api_list.name: Fat Wallet
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://arizona-lottery.p.rapidapi.com/v2/fastplay/143"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "arizona-lottery.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

In the alternative, the winner may choose to be paid $2,500,000 in one lump sum.
